      "acceptanceCriteria": "Minimum n=5 independent experimental replicates per operating point; inter-laboratory reproducibility demonstrated for at least one operating condition.",
      "rationale": "Only n=3 replicates were available per operating point; inter-laboratory reproducibility data are absent. Sample-to-sample variability in blood properties was not characterized. Flagged as epistemic gap; factor not-assessed."
