      "acceptanceCriteria": "Dimensional analysis or direct mapping demonstrates that validation experiment input parameters are equivalent to COU inputs within stated tolerances for all five operating points.",
      "rationale": "Formal equivalency mapping between validation experiment inputs and COU inputs has not been performed. Geometric and flow similarity arguments were made qualitatively in the assessment narrative but no quantitative tolerance analysis was documented. Flagged as epistemic gap; factor not-assessed."
